The paper focuses on a multi-modal task that combines vision and language comprehension, which suggests it could belong to several sub-categories. The use of image and text data implies a connection to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The task also involves machine comprehension, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) or machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the use of metrics and evaluation, which could relate to information retrieval (cs.IR).
